<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.5.7">
<l>kuṉṟamum vāṉum maṇṇuṅ kuḷirpuṉal tiṅka ḷōṭu niṉṟaveñ</l>
<l>cuṭaru mallā nilaikaḷu māya ventai</l>
<l>maṉṟamum vayaluṅ kāvum māṭamum maṇaṅkoṇ ṭeṅkum</l>
<l>teṉṟalvan tulavum nāṅkūrt tirumaṇik kūṭat tāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our father who, besides the hills, the sky, the earth, cool waters,</l>
<l>The moon, and the enduring hot sun, became [all] things that endure,</l>
<l>Is the one in Tirumaṇikkūṭam in Nāṅkūr where the southern breeze wanders,</l>
<l rend="indent">reaching everywhere,</l>
<l>Bringing fragrances to village squares, paddy fields, gardens, and mansions.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
